MODIFICATIONS made by Samuvel Joseph J (https://github.com/Samuvel2407):

  - Added SQLite database dialect support to enable local development without
    Docker or PostgreSQL (backend/internal/app/runtime/db.go, backend/main.go)

  - Fixed URL constructor crash in MarketsByStatusTable.jsx caused by relative
    API_URL value being passed to the JavaScript URL() constructor

  - Fixed React portal mounting error in LoginModal.jsx by dynamically creating
    the #modal-root container when absent from the DOM

  - Configured Vite dev server proxy for /v0 API routes to eliminate hardcoded
    absolute port references (frontend/vite.config.mjs, frontend/src/config.js)

  - Fixed database seeding UNIQUE constraint failure in seed.go by implementing
    Unscoped().Delete() before re-seeding HomepageContent records

  - Overhauled the UI color palette in tailwind.config.js to a modern fintech
    theme (slate background, blue primary, cyan accent)

  - Updated navbar, footer, about page, homepage CMS content, browser title and
    OpenGraph metadata for portfolio presentation

  - Authored comprehensive project documentation (README.md, NOTICE,
    branding_changes_report.md)
